extendedInfo.description: Turn from Super Moron to Complete Genius as you tap and shake your way through all these fun and tricky challenges! Master the game, then laugh as your friends and family struggle with these seemingly simple puzzles! The Super Moron Test is one of the most popular mobile games ever with millions of players worldwide. Play now and experience why The Super Moron Test is an Android Market Store favorite! The Super Moron Test - it's Super fun to FAIL! FEATURES: - Simple, addicting gameplay - Funny characters, sound effects, and music - You will LOVE watching your friends FAIL!
